      code:`# Quality Attribute Scenarios\n\n## Performance\nScenario: 1000 concurrent users browse topics\nStimulus: 1000 simultaneous GET /topics requests\nSystem:   DevMastery API + PostgreSQL + Redis cache\nResponse: All requests served successfully\nMeasure:  95th percentile < 200ms, no errors\n\n## Availability\nScenario: Primary DB failover\nStimulus: PostgreSQL primary node crashes\nSystem:   Supabase managed cluster\nResponse: Automatic failover to replica\nMeasure:  < 30 seconds downtime\n\n## Scalability\nScenario: Traffic spike after viral post\nMeasure:  Auto-scale from 2 to 10 instances < 2 minutes`,
